  "title": "Cloud Engineer - YZ11",
  "description": "<p><strong>Cloud Engineer</strong></p><p><br />Working Days & Hours: 5 days | Mon-Fri: 9am to 6pm <br />Working location: 112 Robinson Road (Tanjong Pagar)<br />Salary: $5500 - $8500</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Responsible for Windows and Linux based IT infrastructure maintenance and implementation;</li><li>Provide technical support and system administration on cloud platform to meet service level objectives;</li><li>Execution of data backup & recovery strategy, system disaster recovery and business continuity of the core systems;</li><li>Follow-up security remediations on cloud platform suggested by cybersecurity team;</li><li>Facilitate cloud operation automation;</li><li>Perform cloud operation task such as health check, capacity monitoring, problem solving and escalation in line with company guidelines or standard operating procedures;</li><li>Configure, document, optimize and support the components of the DevOps infrastructure</li><li>Build automated deployments using configuration management technologies</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Requirement:</strong></p><ul><li>Relevant experiences</li><li>At least bachelor’s degree in Information Technology or its equivalent</li><li>Experience in setting up Windows Server, Linux Server (Ubuntu/CentOS/RHEL), Network configuration/RPM packaging;</li><li>Experience in Blockchain & Web3 infrastructure.</li><li>Experience organizing infrastructure and configuration as code using Ansible, CloudFormation, Terraform or equivalent</li><li>Experience working with modern development pipelines using Bamboo, ArgoCD or similar tools</li><li>Familiarity with containerization technologies (Docker, Kubernetes)</li></ul><p><br />Tan Yen Zhen (Chen Yan Zhen) Reg No: R25138932</p><p>The SupremeHR Advisory Pte Ltd EA No: 14C7279</p>",
